{"tid":228953,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)加蠟味海盜4 天賦的禮物 3X垃圾暴族3","createTime":"2017-05-04T09:45:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-04T14:51:20.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"df5e2b408958cb99fee395f4bb410349924f8fd1","tid":228953,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T09:45:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2F&d=gkHqMR5YDMJAUJmZ80XM4ywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=cb431dee\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/</a> CC台又執柒左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=gkHqMR5YDMJAUJmZ80XM4ywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=bc66b184\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a>可以直接睇到V台<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=gkHqMR5YDMJAUJmZ80XM4ywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=d15daa19\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"http://pic.pimg.tw/mimibao/1180334169.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Fmimibao%2F1180334169.jpg&h=2583f919&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/4/47/Gifted_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F4%2F47%2FGifted_Poster.jpg&h=fb83badb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/7/78/XXx_Return_of_Xander_Cage_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F7%2F78%2FXXx_Return_of_Xander_Cage_Poster.jpg&h=4b8400dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.傑克&middot;史派羅船長（強尼&middot;戴普飾）到達倫敦試圖營救大副約夏米&middot;吉布斯（Joshamee Gibbs，凱文&middot;麥克納利飾）但沒有成功，他被帶到英國國王喬治二世跟前，後者要求傑克帶隊，搶在西班牙人以前找到青春之泉。傑克的死對頭哈克特&middot;巴博沙（Captain Hector Barbossa，傑佛瑞&middot;羅許飾）在失去了「黑珍珠號」和一條腿後加入了英國皇家海軍進行私掠，他將是這次尋寶遠征的指揮官.......<br />\n<br />\n2.在一座佛羅里達州中部的小鎮，七歲的瑪麗在她入學的第一天展現卓越的數學天份。她獲得一筆獎學金供她到專收天才兒童的私立學校就讀，但他的舅舅拒絕接受。他之所以如此，乃因瑪麗的母親曾經是極有前途的數學家，自殺之前致力於納維&ndash;斯托克斯問題（尚未被破解千禧年大獎難題之一）當時瑪麗六個月大。從那時起她的舅舅法蘭克便擔任瑪麗實際上的監護人。他堅信他的妹妹會希望瑪麗過「正常的」童年..<br />\n<br />\n3.故事敘述從極限運動員變成政府特工的桑德&middot;凱吉本被認為已死亡，但因致命戰士翔與他的團隊企圖利用危險的潘多拉盒子為非作歹，使得桑德&middot;凱吉再次被找上，組成新團隊來阻止；而他也發現自己將陷入世界各國政府高層間的勾結和陰謀中..<br />\n<br />\n6 00PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60bd6da226a8ef535df5c1e783f54978462a6ad3","tid":228953,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T10:06:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02736e2033c6094cb2147c21c2b2df5be39d8c71","tid":228953,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T10:37:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5733c1bc2348193db3d105fe5251f7db85499653","tid":228953,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T11:02:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e93e364a28363f3c087fe1fcf6ca658e5406dbae","tid":228953,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T12:19:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets